
<div id="{{ section.id }}" class="badges-section">
  <div class="items">
    <div class="item">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0536/0513/8593/files/Group_18570.jpg?v=1637650622"/>
      <div class="text">
        <div class="title">Discover your inner artist</div>
        <div class="description">Our diamond art subscription is all about inspiration & creativity. Every new painting will encourage you to dive deeper into the fascinating world of art and get acquainted with your tender & dreamy inner self you’ve been hiding for so long!</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item reverse">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0536/0513/8593/files/yoga_1.jpg?v=1637650622"/>
      <div class="text">
        <div class="title">Treat your soul with peace </div>
        <div class="description">Diamond art is more than just beautiful. It is also relaxing. Just imagine coming home after a long day, having your favorite drink, and letting your creativity free…  Our paintings will melt the baggage from the day away and help you feel calm & recharged.</div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0536/0513/8593/files/Group_18572.jpg?v=1637650622"/>
      <div class="text">
        <div class="title">Get closer with your loved ones</div>
        <div class="description">We know - there’s nothing more fulfilling than having a great time with the people you care about. By engaging in this relaxing hobby with your partner or family member, you will feel close & connected no matter how  busy your day was.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  
  #{{ section.id }} *{
    
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} {
   	max-width: 100vw;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    background-color: #245E8D;
    padding-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 35px;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .main-headline{
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 50px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #245E8D;
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 610px;
    padding-left: 10px;
    padding-right: 10px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .divider{
   	margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    max-width: 150px;
    width: 400px;
    min-width: 0px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .sub-headline{
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: normal;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 30px;
    padding-left: 10px;
    padding-right: 10px;
    /* identical to box height, or 120% */

    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;

    color: #3D4246; 
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .items{
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .item {
   	width: 30%; 
    padding: 10px;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .item .title {
	padding-top: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 18px;
    max-width: 180px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    /* or 100% */

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;

    color: #BEFBF4;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .item .description {
	padding-top: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 19px;
    /* or 100% */
	text-align: justify;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .item img {
   	max-width: 80px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 0px;
    background-color: white;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  #{{ section.id }} .item:nth-of-type(2) img {
    padding: 10px;
  }
  
  @media only screen and (max-width: 768px){
    #{{ section.id }} .divider{
      width: 150px;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .main-headline{
    	font-size: 24px;
      	line-height: 40px;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .sub-headline{
     	font-size: 15px; 
      	padding-left: 15px;
      	padding-right: 15px;
    }

    
    #{{ section.id }} .item{
     	width: 100%; 
      	display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
      	align-items: center;
      	padding-top: 0;
      	padding-bottom: 0;
      	padding-left: 20px;
      	padding-right: 20px;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .items{
      	margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item:not(:first-child) {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item.reverse{
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item img{
      	display: inline-block;
     	max-width: 30%; 
      
      	margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item .text div{
        text-align: left;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item .text .title{
        text-align: left;
      	margin-left: 0;
    }
    
    #{{ section.id }} .item.reverse .text{
        text-align: left;
     	padding-right: 20px;
      	
    }
    #{{ section.id }} .item:not(.reverse) .text{
      padding-left: 20px;
     	width: 70%; 
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }
      
</style>

